#

Savory Stuffing with Leeks and Bacon

45 min
$10
300 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 6

Allergens:

GlutenPork

Dietary Tags:

Contains glutenContains pork

Cuisine:

AmericanComfort Food

Course:

Side Dish

Tags:

Comfort foodSide dishEasy recipe

Description

A rich and flavorful stuffing combining the sweetness of leeks and the smokiness of bacon, perfect for any meal.

Ingredients

  • bread cubes (day-old preferred): 6 cups
  • leeks: 2, sliced
  • bacon: 6 slices, chopped
  • chicken broth: 2 cups
  • butter: 4 tablespoons
  • fresh thyme: 1 tablespoon, chopped
  • salt: to taste
  • pepper: to taste
